4. cs.PF (Performance): The paper deals with improving the performance of hybrid platforms by proposing an algorithm for scheduling tasks. This is a core area of research in performance analysis and optimization. 
5. cs.PL (Programming Languages): The paper proposes an algorithm for scheduling tasks on hybrid platforms, which involves designing and implementing algorithms. This is a core area of research in programming languages, where algorithms are often implemented in programming languages.
